page.title: 15Homelife.
page.content: Our house is surrounded by animals and crofts.Every day we work with the animals making sure that they are well fed.When we come home from school we change into our working clothes.After that we help with the animals.We get to play after for about two hours.We check the sheep and then go to bed.We go to bed at ten oclock and get up at seven oclock.When we get up we take the dog for a walk and do the dishes and animals.Then we get ready for school.School starts at 9.30am but we start of from home at nine oclock.
